net.sf.jgcs.jgroups

Class JGroupsMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jgroups.Message
      • net.sf.jgcs.jgroups.JGroupsMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, Message, org.jgroups.util.Streamable

    public class JGroupsMessage
extends org.jgroups.Message
implements Message, Externalizable
    Wraps a JGroups message. It provides a public construtor and implements the Externalizable interface such that it can be serialized. Messages should be created only using the corresponding DataSession.
